Package: shinyplus
Title: Weekly Grocery Planning with PLUS.nl Integration
Version: 1.0.3
Authors@R: c(
  person(given = c("Wikje", "E."),    family = "Berends-Hoekstra",  role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "w.e.berends-hoekstra@umcg.nl"),
  person(given = c("Matthijs", "S."), family = "Berends",           role = c("aut")))
Description: A Shiny web application for planning weekly groceries. 
    Users can select meals for each day, manage recurring and extra items, 
    and combine them into a shopping basket. The app supports integration 
    with the PLUS.nl online supermarket for sending the basket to the user's 
    online shopping cart.
URL: https://github.com/weberends/shinyplus
BugReports: https://github.com/weberends/shinyplus/issues
